3. Post-Class Assignment (Project) (1 hour)

Project: Build a Form Input Validator using Regex:

Create input fields for name, email, phone number, and password

Use regex with quantifiers, grouping, and modifiers to validate inputs

Use. test () to verify inputs and provide user feedback on validity

Use. replace () to auto-format phone numbers on input

Display validation messages dynamically on form submission

Deliverable:

Submit.html and.js files with comments explaining regex usage

Include screenshots or a screen recording demonstrating validation